# =============================================================================
# Frigate secrets — EXAMPLE ONLY.
# Copy to /home/rootuser/frigate_new/secrets/.env and set real values there.
# NEVER commit the real .env to git.
#
# Variable naming: FRIGATE_<INSTANCE>_<SOURCE>_{USER,PASSWORD,HOST}
#   <SOURCE> is a credential/host group defined in inventory/cameras/<inst>.yml.
#   HOST is the camera/DVR IP or hostname (kept out of git on purpose).
# =============================================================================

